      "comment": "HOT ROCKER (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at Sale following on from a second place finish (25.06) there the start prior. Tough to beat if on-song. MISS JECKELL (2) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in third (26.70) at Warragul in a Grade 5 over 460m. Winning chance. LETHAL AVENGER (8) was never in contention last time after drifting back at Sale, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at Sale (24.47) beating Green Frog Cafe in a Grade 5 on April 1. The form out of last race has been strong. One of the main contenders. WEIRD KAREN (3) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
